{"tid":2228633,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"約翰遜與馮德萊恩電話會談 同意加快貿易協議談判","createTime":"2020-10-03T17:30:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-03T17:30:18.000Z","uid":166360,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7a06d9ea6ca14f5227ba5fa7f6169879aa3064e6","tid":2228633,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T17:30:18.000Z","msg":"約翰遜與馮德萊恩電話會談 同意加快貿易協議談判<br />\n2020-10-04 HKT 01:24<br />\n<br />\n&quot;......英國首相約翰遜與歐盟委員會主席馮德萊恩舉行電話會談，雙方同意加快談判，化解阻礙建立新貿易夥伴關係的重大分歧，兩人亦同意定期交流。<br />\n<br />\n會議後，雙方發表聯合聲明，指出英國及歐盟都認同達成協議的重要性，將成為英歐未來戰略關係的穩健基礎......&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1552928-20201004.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1552928-20201004.htm&d=YLq6vaBnyeHQX05GIPWJdreFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=828f7657\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1552928-20201004.htm&h=23633fe2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1552928-20201004.htm</a>"}]}